    "The VAE was used to dimensionally reduce the raw radar data, and the regression network was used to map the compressed features to the output space.",
    "Taking the raw radar signal as input, the DNN directly predicted the rectangular boundary of the target.",
    "Waveform designISAC waveform design aims at obtaining the dual-functional waveform to achieve the dual services.",
    "However, the existing waveform design schemes often face the challenges of high complexity and may not be suitable for the time-varying scenario [238].",
    "AI is considered an effective enabler for intelligent waveform design due to its powerful nonlinear fitting capability, low complexity, and high adaptability to the dynamic environment."
